Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vector 21" newscast] </F>
  [Text] President Carlos Salinas de Gortari received 
important visitors at Los Pinos this afternoon. Jaime Serra 
Puche, Mexican secretary of commerce and industrial development, 
U.S. Commerce Secretary Mickey Kantor, and Roy MacLaren, 
