  [Text] Long Live the 22d EGP [Poor People's Guerrilla Army] 
Anniversary. 
  Exactly 22 years ago, our heroic and combative revolutionary 
POOR PEOPLE'S GUERRILLA ARMY-EGP-emerged. Today it is an active 
