  LONG LIVE THE CERJ! ["Rujunel Junam" 
Ethnic 
  Communities Council] 
  LONG LIVE THE ORGANIZED PEOPLE! 
  URNG 
  LONG LIVE THE POOR PEOPLE'S ARMY 
  19 JANUARY, 22 YEARS OF STRUGGLE 
  TO THE GUATEMALAN PEOPLE AND ALL SECTORS OF SOCIETY: TO 
FIND THE POLITICAL SOLUTION TO THE INTERNAL ARMED CONFLICT AND 
TO THE SERIOUS SITUATION WE ARE LIVING IT IS URGENT: 
  THAT YOU JOIN THE REVOLUTIONARY MOVEMENT 
  THAT YOU VOTE NO IN THE REFERENDUM 
  THAT YOU SUPPORT THE NEGOTIATIONS 
  DIALOGUE IS STRUGGLE AND NOT SURRENDER! 
  [signed] Guatemalan National Revolutionary Unity. 

