<H3> <TI>   New Democratic Alliance Announces Presidential Ticket </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2301023294 Panama City Circuito RPC Radio in Spanish 0209 
GMT 23 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2301023294 </F>
<F P=104>  Panama City Circuito RPC Radio </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At the residence of Panamenist Party Vice President 
Alfredo Arias in Altos del Golf, where negotiations to establish 
the progovernment presidential ticket were conducted, it has 
been disclosed that the Democratic Alliance has been formed. 
The Alliance's presidential ticket is as follows: 
  Presidential candidate, Mireya Moscoso; first vice 
presidential candidate, Dr. Arnulfo Escalona; and second vice 
presidential candidate, Dr. Jose Teran Sitton of the Liberal 
Party. 

